*Declare a variable of type date and give it halloween day.

REPORT Z_ABAP101_019.

*We can declare a variable of type 'D'
*(date) & assign the date value for Haloween.

DATA haloween_date TYPE D VALUE '20231031'.

*This line declares a variable named 'haloween_date'
*of type 'D' & initializes it with the date '2023-10-31',
*which represents Halloween day.
